# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Admin panel security
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Prevent directory listing
Options -Indexes

# OPTIONAL: Restrict admin panel to school IP addresses only.
# Uncomment and replace with your school's actual IP range to lock this
# page down so only people on school wifi/network can access it.
#
# <RequireAll>
#     Require ip 192.168.1.0/24
# </RequireAll>
